            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "We loaded back up into the taxi and headed to our next destination -  the Moray Incan Ruins. We were literally only able to spend about twenty minutes here, but it was enough time to walk halfway down to the ruins and take some great photos."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/BIRU-WP-20150806T150859GMT-0500-1024x768.jpg",
