                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " It is unknown what the purpose of the circular formations was, but many archaeologists think that it could have been an agricultural experimentation center. For size reference, notice how small the children climbing up the ruins look in the picture below!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "attrs": {
              "src": "images/BIRU-WP-20150806T151647GMT-0500-1024x768.jpg",
              "alt": "Cuzco / Peru - 8/6/15",
              "title": null
            },
            "marks": [
              {
